name: DELOREAN (DLN)
description:
Delorean Coin ($DLN) is for the future! A future where you’re going – you wont need roads.

A future with holographic sharks and a future with flying cars. So buckle up, flux capacitor on and enjoy the ride! 

A recent study has shown that more members of the global population will be using mobile phones (5.5 billion) than bank accounts (5.4 billion), running water (5.3 billion), or landlines (2.9 billion).
